:'''Cipher:''' Hey there, Gray Mystery! Making the rounds, huh?
:'''Cipher:''' Don't overdo it. Life's easy here. Sip some tea, feel the breeze, and enjoy the rare vacation. Isn't it awesome?
:<!--Custom String Trigger: Wait_Option_803510637_224-->
:<!--Custom String Listener: Wait_Option_803510637_224-->
:{{DIcon|Talk}} Sounds like the good life.
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_835163704-->
::'''Cipher:''' It is! This is my dream for retirement, slow and peaceful. I swear I'm not lying.
::'''Cipher:''' Well, spending time with all those little critters... I think they're slowing me down! My reflexes aren't what they used to be, and I've even picked up their little "mem" speech quirk.
::'''Cipher:''' Use it or lose it, huh? Think I'll ever get back into my old groove... Mem?
:;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
:{{DIcon|Exit}} Let's catch up another time!
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_835163708-->
